but I didn't use all of the quotes that I memorized

00:01:02.440 --> 00:01:04.359
because I used essay plans,

00:01:04.360 --> 00:01:05.879
and I would only use relevant quotes

00:01:05.880 --> 00:01:08.100
or short quotes that I could just easily

00:01:08.360 --> 00:01:11.220
write down and explain briefly.

